title: MMBN5: Team Colonel Any% No ASE

text.text:
ACDC 1: 
Grab GMDs
Grab BMD (800 Zenny)
Jack in to PC, do tutorials

ACDC 2: 
Grab GMDs
Buy HP Memory from shop
Yai’s room: Talk to her, turn on furnace, jack into her HP and get BMD (RegUp2)
Dex’s room: Talk to him, jack into his HP grab BMDs (RegUp1 and HP Memory)
Jack into tree: Grab BMD (HP memory)
Jack into right chip statue: Grab BMD (HP Memory)
Talk to trash can for RegUp1
Go into lab and end up in ACDC areas
Activate SneakRun and go all the way to end of ACDC 2 and win battle
Run into locked door in the lab
Dad’s lab, get his ID from desk, jack into his comp and grab BMD (RegUp2)
R -> O -> T -> A -> L -> BLANK   OWL RAT
H -> C -> L -> D -> A -> BLANK   DOCK HALL
H -> E -> M -> T -> I -> A -> BLANK   HIP TOE ARM

Sort reverse MB,
First WideSword <-> First Sword,
Slot 1 <-> Cannon A,
Reg AreaGrab,
Remove recovs,
Add good things
Talk to Baryl then go to sleep

Go to FurnaceComp, grab BMD  (HP Memory) go straight up

Run to the end of the screen

Enter Mine and go straight up to blue elevator
Go up the ramp and jack into the thing, get MineKey
Go back through the door, get HP Memory from crates
Go to DrillComps and fight doors
Grab all GMDs in DrillComps, and fight Drills for up to 4 DrillArms
Nothing to grab, just GMDs and DrillArms

Straight path clearing clouds to Oran 2

Gray to Prog, then towards SciLab2
Straight until Prog, clear with him
Gray, down to white, yellow, clear with Prog
Up to thunder, right to yellow and clear with Prog
Left to 2 black clouds, clear with prog

Back up to white, gray, gray, gray

Fight green navi,
